Package main.model.request

Class Enquiry

java.lang.Object
main.model.request.Enquiry
All Implemented Interfaces:
Displayable, Model, Request, Mappable
public class Enquiry extends Object implements Request
The Enquiry class represents an inquiry request made by a student regarding a camp. It implements the Request interface, providing methods to manage and retrieve information about the inquiry request.
